{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_leizi_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_leizi_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"司雷霆者","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"一桩弹劾旧案，一位已经致仕的少卿，一项有悖炎律的正义之举。大理寺麟青砚，肃政院太合、解真须在一个时辰内协商出最后的结果。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_leizi_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["太合","？？？","麟青砚","解真"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_bg_25_g06_mountainroad_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","duration":"1","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"......","id":11,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":12},{"type":"charslot","id":13},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":14},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","duration":"1","id":15},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"呼——","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"辛苦你跑一趟。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"今天正好轮到我当值......","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"太合，有什么事情不能在肃政院的官署里说？","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"charslot","id":24},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_flag","volume":"1","id":25},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","duration":"1","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":27},{"type":"charslot","id":28},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":29},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"r","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"原来还是为虞少卿的事。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"麟青砚少卿就这么急于处置自己的前辈？","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"这件事也是肃政院御史台的职责所在，解真御史未免太过怠慢。","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"charslot","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"......是我召二位来此。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"肃政院监察百官，纵然其人已致仕返乡，在任期间所犯之事，也当追究法办。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"当年虞澄少卿在弹劾琅珆知府时伪造证据一事，干系重大，二位此前已协商多次，未有定论。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"约一个时辰后，虞澄少卿便会抵达此处......","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":44},{"type":"charslot","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":46},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"r","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"你竟然瞒着我直接召回了他！","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......不愧是太合。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":51},{"type":"charslot","id":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"此事不宜再拖。如何处置，二位须在一个时辰内有个定论。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"若秉公断案，那我等便于此间代三法司会审，当行炎律。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"若施之以柔，虞少卿上山时，烦劳二位回避，让我二人叙旧。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"此山离京城不过二十里。入京之后，事情便再无转圜的余地。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"charslot","id":59},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":60},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"r","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":65},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":66},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":67},{"type":"charslot","id":68},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":69},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":71},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":72},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","duration":"1.5","id":73},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","duration":"1.5","id":74},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":75},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"我还是那句话，你未免太不讲情理。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"我也说过很多次了，麟青砚只是行大理寺少卿当行之事。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"十年前，虞澄少卿巡检天下刑狱，过琅珆时弹劾当地知府，历一年三月，琅珆知府下狱身死。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"而我在整理卷宗时，发现了其中的疑点。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"三个月前我去到琅珆，反复查证......当年虞少卿弹劾所用的账册、名录等关键物证，确实系伪造。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"这件事证据确凿，辩无可辩。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"我并没有要否认这桩旧案。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"只是请问少卿大人，那位琅珆知府，难道不该被弹劾吗？","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"他在任多年，欺上瞒下，侵吞朝廷拨款，是否属实？","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"他私发地方政令，屡次巧征新税，是否也是“辩无可辩”的事？","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"他拦截伸冤的百姓，贿赂督察官员，虚报民情，又为祸一方了多长时间？","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"虞澄在弹劾状上列举了他十多条罪状，有没有哪一条是编造的呢？","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"都属实。","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":95},{"type":"charslot","id":96},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"虞少卿若是污人清白，我等又何须在此相商？","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"琅珆知府弹劾案，牵连琅珆、京城及巡检部门官员有嫌疑者近十人，经查俱无虚告，朝堂震动，地方肃然，风气为之一改。","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":100},{"type":"charslot","id":101},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":102},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"r","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"我听说那阵子，百姓投来的感谢信函，在大理寺和肃政院码了厚厚几摞。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"客观来说，这难道不是一件大快人心的好事？","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"换言之，虞少卿所作所为，结果上难道不是有利于民？","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"太合，你说呢？","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"charslot","id":112},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"然。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":115},{"type":"charslot","id":116},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"r","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"更何况，你似乎误解了我的意思。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"我从来没说不会处理这件事。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"你所谓的处理......","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"大理寺会将虞澄从浩然阁中除名，户部将追回他的致仕金，他返乡后享有的一应优待，也将全部取消。","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"更者，如果虞澄的亲眷将来入仕，朝廷也会多作考量。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"同时，此事将知会刑部、肃政院及大理寺，三法司在任的所有大小官员，须引以为戒。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"如果虞澄真是个大奸大恶之徒，用不着你说，在捉拿他下狱之前，我还得先用手里这牵丝刃折磨他个十回八回。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"但他操劳一生，是人人称颂的好官。他今年快七十了，我们姑且保他一个安稳的晚年，有何不可？","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":130},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"秘而不宣，小惩小戒......对天下而言，其行未彰，其恶未诛。说什么“有何不可”？","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"r","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"太合，你觉得呢？","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":137},{"type":"charslot","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"l","id":139},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"l","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"我......","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"r","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......你也是这个想法？","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"太合，我清楚你的为人，是非分明，公事公办，可从来没有这么多弯弯绕的心思，所以才能在离开军伍后这么快便升任监察御史......","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"怎么这次？","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"l","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"青砚少卿过奖。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"实不相瞒......","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"暂且不论官阶，放下立场，我对虞少卿当年之所作所为，唯有钦佩。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"那知府劣迹斑斑，多年来，琅珆并非无人与之抗争，却最终无声无息。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"盖因其行事滴水不漏，上下打点，手眼通天。若非别无他法，虞少卿何必出此下策？","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"在那桩案子里，他其实押上了自己的身家性命。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"如此浩然正气，如此舍生忘死之英勇，不逊我那些沙场上的袍泽。","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"r","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"l","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"......所以，今日之事，只能交予二位定夺。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":158},{"type":"charslot","id":159},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"啧，太合，我还挺欣赏你这柔情的一面的。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"我同样敬佩虞少卿的为人。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":166},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"你们看到前面那棵树了吗？","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"charslot","id":172},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_bg_25_g08_pavilion.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":174},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":175},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15side/m_sys_bitw_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":176,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"4.5","id":177},{"type":"text","text":"三人转过一个山角，视野陡然开阔。","id":178},{"type":"text","text":"太合与解真顺着麟青砚的视线看过去，悬崖百丈，云雾扼断前路，一棵瘦直的松树傲然挺立，露出积雪也掩藏不住的翠色。","id":179},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"一年前，我刚从天师府来到大理寺，虞少卿是我最为敬慕的前辈。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"他要返乡，我坚持送他一程，他绕路带我来爬了这座山。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"难怪你今天来得比我和太合都早。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"那棵松树，是他多年前亲手种下的。","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"原来如此。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"那时候的虞少卿还是个愣头青，登高远眺，眼前只有云遮雾罩。猛然间阳光透过，将阴霾一扫而空，天地清朗......","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"他想到自己马上就要进入京城，赴大理寺就职，心里面感慨万千。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"他立誓要为天下人伸张正义，成为炎律的最后一道隘口，不让任何人蒙冤受屈，于是种下一棵松苗以明心迹。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"好一个虞少卿！","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"是啊。那棵小小的松苗已经长成了如此挺拔的树，前辈他也同样对得起自己当年的抱负。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"虞澄是大理寺有史以来最杰出的少卿，审冤断错无数，琅珆知府一案并不是他经手过最难的案子......","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"他只错了这一回。但他错了这一回。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"......","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"一棵孤松长成这样，多么难得。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"无论是谁，一路攀登，猛然看见有这么一棵树，挺身入云，饱历风雪而不折，心里都会为之一振。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"麟青砚少卿，推倒这一棵树，会冷了多少登山之人的热血呢？","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"解真御史话中有话。","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"我想要压下这桩旧案，不单单是为了保下虞澄一人。","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"青砚少卿刚就任大理寺少卿不过一年，便彻查前任少卿的所有卷宗，在他致仕之后召回定罪。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"那下一任大理寺少卿，是不是上任后也该查一查你呢？","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"青砚少卿只是例行整理卷宗时偶然......","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"是。但又有什么区别？","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"你我应该清楚得很，再清白的人，也经不起“查”。更何况是官身。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"......","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"你们想想，如果这种事成了惯例，大小官员人人自危，心有远虑，做起事情便会束手束脚。","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"毕竟一旦失之偏颇，就成了把柄。同僚也好，后继者也好，指不定哪天被有心人发现，自己就得锒铛入狱。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"长此以往，谁还敢在任上有所作为？","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"......","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"青砚少卿，三法司不是天师府，我们往往要权衡更多东西。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"解真，你何必偷换概念？","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"身为大理寺少卿，伪造证据，这件事的性质，到了你口中，竟然只是“失之偏颇”？","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"更何况，你的说法，恕我难以苟同。","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"嗯？","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"未有作为，而思保全？","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"我幼年初学雷法，天师便教导我，“司雷霆者，必先敬畏其威，否则必有自伤之日”。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"三法司中，肃政院监察百官，大理寺复核刑狱，每个官员、每桩案子，后面都需要一双眼睛、一道隘口。","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"那我们这些行监察之职的人，身后是不是也需要另一双眼睛、另一道隘口呢？世上没有完美的制度，不可能这样层叠循环下去。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"所以我们这些人，最先应该监察的，其实是自己。不然如何保证律法能真正护佑每一个炎国百姓？","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"我们都在三法司当差，你未必不清楚这个道理！","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"难道，法不容情？","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"绝情的究竟是你，还是炎律？！","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"执炎律者，若有律不依，那立炎律何用？！","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"二位不必如此过激......","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"我必须追究这桩旧案，同样不单单是为了处置虞澄一人。","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"虞少卿当年在琅珆，面对那个劣迹斑斑却滴水不漏的知府，为了伸张正义，不得已用了“偏颇”的手段，似乎情有可原。","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"换作你我，未必不会做出同样的选择。","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"可如果日后我们面对的是更加暧昧的情况呢？可如果日后我们有意为恶呢？","id":260,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"是否更容易动用些“偏颇”的手段，去放过一个坏人，去构陷一个好人？","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"毕竟，为恶，要简单得多。","id":262,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"国之法度，定人生死。你我身在其位，便容不得半点行差踏错！","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"......","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":268},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":269},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"青砚少卿所言，让人醍醐灌顶。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"律法面前，无“事宜从权”一说，这还是太傅当年对我的教诲。","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"若因对虞少卿的钦佩之情，有伤炎律之仪......因私废公，是我荒唐了。","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":274},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":275},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"算来，虞少卿也该到了。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"解真御史可还有话说？","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_041","focus":"m","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"......","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"话都说到了这份上......这桩案子由青砚少卿提起，决定权当然也在她。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"我承认你说的在理。","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"解真","text":"但最后还是想请二位想想，弹劾虞澄，相比当年弹劾那位琅珆知府，影响只大不小。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_041.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_040","focus":"m","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"......","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"太合","text":"既然如此，请少卿定夺。","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_040.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"m","id":288},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"所谓法者，便是悬在人们心上与头顶的那道雷。","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"雷声惊蛰，天地通明。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"麟青砚","text":"若此雷不落，麟青砚难为大理寺少卿。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_039_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":293},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_thunders_amb","volume":"0.7","id":295},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_flag","volume":"1","id":298},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":299},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":300},{"type":"text","text":"白日惊雷，羽兽骤起疾飞，积雪从枝丫间扑簌簌落下，那棵青松依然挺拔，又多了几分翠色。","id":301},{"type":"text","text":"山下，远来的客人刚刚下车。他怔怔抬头，良久未曾挪动一步。","id":302},{"type":"dialog","id":303},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":306},{"type":"character","id":307},{"type":"charslot","id":308},{"type":"image","id":309}],"characters":["太合","？？？","麟青砚","解真"]}